{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227950, "create_time": 1655464804, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "医学院本部是黄了吗", "timestamp": 1655464804}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227951, "create_time": 1655464812, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "本来就没有结婚，只是谈了一场难有结果的恋爱", "timestamp": 1655464812}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227953, "create_time": 1655464856, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "渣男！", "timestamp": 1655464856}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227958, "create_time": 1655465038, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 正解", "timestamp": 1655465038}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227967, "create_time": 1655465150, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "协和看不上清华", "timestamp": 1655465150}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 227989, "create_time": 1655465495, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "协和医学院离不开清华的本科招生（否则分数线肯定大幅下降），清华医学院也离不开协和医院的临床培养（长庚是什么水平懂的都懂），所以现状就是各取所需", "timestamp": 1655465495}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228017, "create_time": 1655466040, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "协和养鱼呢，清华死心了而已", "timestamp": 1655466040}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228026, "create_time": 1655466102, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "此外，协和系统实际上不止有八年制、协和、阜外、肿瘤医院等优质资源，还有基础所、护理学院和京外的一些研究所。清华基本上只想要优质资源（当然这是完全不可能的），协和又自视甚高，所以从合作开始两边就根本没有完全合并的可能性。", "timestamp": 1655466102}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228036, "create_time": 1655466285, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "接下来很长一段时间两边应该还会维持现状，除非清华真的能吞掉首医（这个传闻前几年出现过，但现在已经没有声音了）。", "timestamp": 1655466285}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228124, "create_time": 1655467182, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 首医也看不上清华，除非清华同意首医像现在的协和这样外加十年XX亿元经费投入。", "timestamp": 1655467182}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228139, "create_time": 1655467434, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "", "timestamp": 1655467434}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228147, "create_time": 1655467480, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "医学院建设最关键的就是临床医院，但北京的医院早就被北医、协和和首医三个系统分完了。从零开始建设医院和从零开始建设一个学科还是有很大的区别的，前者并不是砸钱请人就可以办到的。清华现在基本就是一边慢慢经营长庚，一边找合作医院培养自己的学生，今年开始会加入很多国外的医院，不知道效果如何。", "timestamp": 1655467480}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228172, "create_time": 1655467733, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 清华想要的其实只有医院，对其他部分是完全不感兴趣，首医要是能同意才见鬼了", "timestamp": 1655467733}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228378, "create_time": 1655470501, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 不想要学校不至于，不想要学校牌子是真的。医学院校和附属医院是一体的，你只要来一个医院，学校老师不要走，拿空壳子么？反过来说学校老师都跟着医院走了，那首医不也是空壳子了？清华合并首医是奔着医院去的不错，但是你想要医院肯定学校也得要，只不过清华只想彻底吞并、不想让首医学协和罢了。", "timestamp": 1655470501}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 228391, "create_time": 1655470697, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 清华这边临床最大的问题是规培以及延伸出来的就业。医院讲圈子，清华现在出来的医生除了自己的附属医院，在其他圈子是被排挤的，基本上很难走到医生就业那条路。实验室一个清华临床的博士后就极其尴尬，接着和北京医院的关系走完了规培，但是还是没法在业内就业，只能去企业做医疗业务咨询/行研这种。", "timestamp": 1655470697}], "create_time": 1655464687, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655470697, "likenum": 14, "n_attentions": 14, "n_comments": 15, "pid": 67279, "poll": null, "reply": 15, "text": "所以清华和协和是注定要离婚了吗", "timestamp": 1655464687}}